Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这粒子束是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认定3架Gundam Throne为助长纷争的对象 开始武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 开始驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人 这些机体 怎么算得上Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 约翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗 Exia的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妨碍我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑混乱了吗 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 应战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚·爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 摧毁目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在和Throne战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才 Virtue似乎也加入了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连提艾利亚也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam间居然自相残杀 搞不好就会两败俱伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不挺好吗 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体的行事方针实在让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是不错的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们的行动也可能是计划的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们采取这样的行动也许也在计划之内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯发来了紧急暗号通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求指示中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回复 如果可能的话请制止双方的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也同意自身临场应变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上也就是随他怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可称不上战术预测员之名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚呢 出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待在这里保护托勒密 既然事已至此 这里也不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说内心充满了出击的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 尽做些出人意料的事 那个不听话的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 没能制止 没能制止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多亏此 斯米拉琪小姐也下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也明白刹那的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想成为Gundam 成为根绝战争的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是充满大干一场的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 Exia对新型的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红龙 我认为 只要这个世界能改变就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管采取何种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向第三阶段的转移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能回头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵型S32
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会有和你使用阵型的一天到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia Virtue 继续与Throne交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在使用战术阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从S32 D07 到F52
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚和刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 合体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为会给你时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你这机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 机体的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与维塔连机的机体全部处于我的控制之下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam Nadleeh真正的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅授予提艾利亚的Gundam机师的审判系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:39.87,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1466,990)}Trial System
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不配做Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 万死难辞其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判系统居然被强制解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于Level7区域的部分资料被篡改了 这数据区域到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连我都无法访问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然维塔里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是三对三了 要公平竞赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 尼娜 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam间内斗的话就会阻碍计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们相比 你有应该先解决的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是 尼尔·狄兰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔·狄兰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 居然掌握了我的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过维塔读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level7的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 让你不惜成为Gundam机师也想要对其复仇的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯共和国的反政府游击队 KPSA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个组织的成员中 有一个叫 索兰·依伯拉罕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰·依伯拉罕 行动名 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟说是刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 他就是杀死你父母和妹妹的那个组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不共戴天的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7台Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是他们的对手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行无谓的战斗 消耗军力的话 我方阵营的经济也会受损
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 只有接受他们的要求 解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话各国的主权也会因此崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称是天行者的人通过网络联系了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还提供了组织的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 内部分裂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似上帝没有抛弃我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到攻击的IRIS公司的厂址前聚集了众多的受害者家属
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深地沉浸在悲痛的气氛中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行攻击的三台MS是新型的Gundam 对于这种过激行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 鲜花我放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 回日本去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘课可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你来陪着我很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能一直这样下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把露易丝一个人丢下什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈的梦想是去宇宙工作对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要因为自己而让沙慈的梦想无法实现啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在在一起 以后也会痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直感到自卑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈会不断地后悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我能把梦想寄托给沙慈么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去实现梦想吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请实现我的梦想吧… 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方睡 可是会感冒的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?啊 你…你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介绍应从男生开始才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?啊 那个…我是沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝·哈勒维 请多指教哦 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就直呼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 也不是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 拜托你做这么麻烦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是拉古那·哈维啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线性轨道列车事业的总裁 国际经济团的领导嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有建造MS的财力 也能自由使用轨道电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 取材就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 对方可是我们的大财主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随随便便出手的话会完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才秘密调查的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会收手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到了线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经是KPSA所属
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯出身?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击队的少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 崔尼蒂说过的事情是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事实!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母和妹妹 被卷入KPSA的自杀恐怖炸弹袭击而死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从伴随着太阳能发电计划的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界规模的石油输出规制开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是已经不要再依赖化石燃料生存了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最受影响的是中东诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被输出规制导致国家经济的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民陷入了贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷和饥饿让人们将希望寄托在神明身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对神的代言人听信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是些追求财富与权利的肤浅之见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是导致了那场长达20年的太阳能纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住在神明之地的人民的圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自认为主宰一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然单方面控制了出口管理的国联也是伪善
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是神明和宗教并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳能发电系统也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是世界却因此走向畸形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你被KPSA利用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行着本非所愿的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这畸形的世界影响了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了家人 一个人都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以接受成为机师的现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道这其中的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的所作所为和恐怖活动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去斩断引发暴行的锁链而是战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是为了阻止悲剧重演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要彻底地改变这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有压倒性的力量并用其抑制世界的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受改变世界将受到的因果报应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是此前我还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 此刻我几乎无法抑制干掉你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给我的家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的怨念得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾信仰神明 被迫去信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说这不是你的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上没有神明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!?为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上没有神明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可没回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰神明 然后否定神明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙歇斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在莫拉利亚所属PMC
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间军事企业?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干完游击队然后去当佣兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是单纯的战争狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莫拉利亚的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 原来那时从驾驶舱走出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想确认他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道他的神明在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不再信仰神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我…到现在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想听一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我干掉你就不能如愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我校正这畸形的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我还活着 我就会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非作为索兰·依伯拉罕而是作为天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶着Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太傻瓜了 我都射不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个了不得的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的称赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:37.20,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}非洲大陆西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会被Gundam袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连kiss都献出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求Laguna下指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能会和Gundam再交战了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:01.94,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}南极大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨幅变化导致世界平衡的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人欢喜有人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到死去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 变革之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此份痛苦 谁人知晓




